[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（投稿したコラボ動画は大好評。互いの視聴者層を\n　取り込んで、再生数も大きく伸びた）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00885",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（その後に投稿した動画も、\n　どんどん勢いを増していき……そして）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00886",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（審査の日が、やって来た）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00887",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うう……社長、まだ来ないの？\nそろそろ結果が出ててもおかしくないよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00888",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "やっぱり不合格だったのかな！？\nああ、もう！　待つことしかできないなんて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00889",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "落ち着きなさいよ、かっこ悪い。\nドーンと構えてなさい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00890",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そういうヨハナだって、先ほどから時計ばかり\n見ているでござるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00891",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "うるさいわね……その口、\nテープで塞いでやろうかしら……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00892",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "や、やめてくだされヨハナー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00893",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あら、元気ですわね。\nもっと緊張しているかと思いましたが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00894",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "この二人が緊張でおかしくなっていまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00895",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あらあら。では、早く結果を知らせませんと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00896",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "お願い！　早く教えて！\n……ううん、やっぱやめて！　まだ覚悟が！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00897",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……先に言っておきますわね。\n皆さんは、よく頑張りました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00898",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "この短期間で、ここまでたくさんのファンを獲得し、\n人気を得たのは素晴らしい功績ですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00899",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "たとえ結果がどうであったとしても、\n自分に誇りを持つように",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00900",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……合格ですわ！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00901",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……ほ、本当でござるか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00902",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ここで嘘をつく必要はないでしょう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00903",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "じゃあ、怖がらせるんじゃないわよ！\n何が「先に言っておきますわね」よ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00904",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "とにかく、選ばれたんだよね……アタシたち！\nやったー！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00905",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "っと……キューン殿から？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00906",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……おお！？　『ＱＥジーンズ』も合格との連絡が！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00907",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "まさか、どっちも受かるなんて……奇跡ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00908",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "よかったね！　それじゃあ、\nフェスでもキューンたちに会えるんだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00909",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "さて、改めて……おめでとうございます、三人とも。\n今回の結果に関しては、先ほどの言葉の通りですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00910",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "しかし、気を抜いてはなりませんわ！\n次に待ち構えているのは、あのカウントダウンフェス",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00911",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そこで成功を収め、多くの観客の心を掴んでこそ、\n『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』の未来があるのです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00912",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "明日からは厳しい練習の時間が続くでしょう。\n今夜は早めに寝て、ゆっくり休みなさいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00913",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "そっか……冷静に考えたらそうだよね。\nここが終わりじゃないんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00914",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "むしろここがスタートライン！\nさあ、明日からも頑張るわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00915",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "イザナ/鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00916",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00917",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……鬼門。あなたはこの後少し、お時間よろしくて？\nあなた宛てに手紙が来ているのです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00918",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたの、ご家族から",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00919",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "…………！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00920",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]